text: Edmund Armand Wingo (1895–1964) was a Canadian professional baseball player. He appeared in one game in Major League Baseball for the Philadelphia Athletics during the 1920 season as a catcher. ==References== Category:1895 births Category:1964 deaths Category:Baseball people from Quebec Category:Canadian expatriate baseball players in the United States Category:Major League Baseball catchers Category:Philadelphia Athletics players Category:Valleyfield/Cap-de-la-Madeleine Madcaps players Category:Quebec Bulldogs (baseball) players Category:Outremont Canadiens players Category:Ottawa-Hull Senators players Category:Major League Baseball players from Canada Category:People from Sainte-Anne-de-Bellevue, Quebec
